    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 guidance for Class II devices. Primary validation result demonstrates NIH agreement within 15% and RH = 0.87 satisfying the acceptance criterion. High assurance level declared based on exceeding discretization error requirements and breadth of verification activities. The secondary shear stress validation result provides supporting evidence for spatial localization of hemolysis risk. Credibility package accepted for regulatory submission supporting 510(k) substantial equivalence argument.",
